@startuml
actor "Manager" as MGR
boundary "UI Preferensi" as UI
control "API /api/bwm/preferensi" as API
database "Supabase\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

== LIST PREFERENSI ==
MGR -> UI: Buka halaman Preferensi
UI -> API: GET /api/bwm/preferensi
activate API
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM preferensi_bwm ORDER BY created_at DESC
DB --> API: [{ id, nama, best, worst, bo.., ow.., is_active }]
API --> UI: { data: [...] }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Tampil daftar preferensi + badge aktif

== BUAT PREFERENSI BARU ==
MGR -> UI: Klik "Buat Preferensi Baru"
UI -> MGR: Dialog form (nama, best, worst, BO, OW)
MGR -> UI: Isi & submit
note right: Validasi client:\nbest != worst\nBO[best] = 1\nOW[worst] = 1

UI -> API: POST /api/bwm/preferensi
activate API
note right: Validasi server:\nrange 1-9,\nbest/worst valid
API -> DB: INSERT INTO preferensi_bwm (nama, best_criteria, worst_criteria, bo_c1.., ow_c1..)
DB --> API: { id, ... }
API --> UI: { message: "Preferensi berhasil dibuat" }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Toast sukses

== AKTIFKAN PREFERENSI ==
MGR -> UI: Klik "Aktifkan" pada preferensi
UI -> API: PATCH /api/bwm/preferensi { id, is_active: true }
activate API
API -> DB: UPDATE preferensi_bwm SET is_active=false WHERE is_active=true
API -> DB: UPDATE preferensi_bwm SET is_active=true WHERE id=$1
DB --> API: OK
API --> UI: { message: "Preferensi diaktifkan" }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Badge berubah hijau

== HAPUS PREFERENSI ==
MGR -> UI: Klik ikon hapus -> konfirmasi
UI -> API: DELETE /api/bwm/preferensi?id=$1
activate API
API -> DB: DELETE FROM preferensi_bwm WHERE id=$1
DB --> API: OK
API --> UI: { message: "Preferensi berhasil dihapus" }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Toast sukses
@enduml
